<seg id="612">THISSEGMENTISINTENTIONAL LEFT BLACK</seg>
<seg id="613">On the basis of the information contained in UST pre-declarations or UST declarations as well as audit reports, qualified auditors select the cases to be examined and ensure the correct taxation.</seg>
<seg id="614">In order to reduce UST revenue losses and at the same time increase the risk of being discovered for unreliable entrepreneurs, appropriate management processes and risk management systems should be introduced.</seg>
